com.adobe.icc.dbforms.obj

Class Asset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.icc.dbforms.obj.Asset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILocalizable, ILocalizationResourceContainer, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContainerLayout, DataModule, Form, Letter

    public abstract class Asset
extends Object
implements Serializable, ILocalizable, ILocalizationResourceContainer
    Base class (POJO) for all asset types in the system, like DataModule, TextModule, ListDataModule, etc.

    Contains basic common attributes for an Asset, such as name, description, version, etc.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
